oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Mejora e integración de Netatmo Weathermap sobre la actual aplicación Android Netatmo WeatherStation
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The aim of this section is to introduce Netatmo, the company where this project has been carried out. This project is related to a particular product called Netatmo Weather Station. For understanding the context of the project, this particular product is further explained. Finally the project is introduced.
